author: CBR
description:
Star Trek: The Last Starship finally lets us inside Kirk’s head — and it raises even bigger questions about who he is now. 

The writers tease what Kirk remembers, how he reacts to a darker universe, and, of course, his guitar solo!

🎙️ Clip from CBR’s Heroes Journey Podcast – Episode 9.
